IMPORTANT NOTE ABOUT MOVIE SOUNDTRACKS:

This software provides suggestions for movie soundtracks to accompany board game
sessions. The actual movie soundtracks, music, and audio content are NOT included
in this software and remain the intellectual property of their respective copyright
holders.

Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining proper licenses for any copyrighted music they choose to play
- Respecting copyright laws in their jurisdiction
- Using only legally obtained audio content
- Following fair use guidelines for any preview functionality

The software authors do not provide, distribute, or endorse any specific
copyrighted audio content. All soundtrack suggestions are provided for
informational purposes only to help users discover music that might enhance
their board gaming experience.